comments: Wade (CLE) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Jones (NOP) and cleanly blocks the shot attempt.
Valanciunas (NOP) makes marginal contact to Love's (CLE) back while rebounding.
Temple (NOP) makes hand on ball contact to deflect the ball away from Okoro (CLE).
Wade (CLE) makes marginal contact with his forearm to Temple's (NOP) body that doesn't affect his SBQR as he makes the pass.
Jones (NOP) makes contact with Okoro's (CLE) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Valanciunas (NOP) establishes his screening position in Garland's (CLE) path and absorbs the contact.
Love (CLE) and Valanciunas (NOP) engage and disengage while rebounding.
Okoro (CLE) and Valanciunas (NOP) briefly get tangled in the post and the contact is marginal.
Replay review of the defensive goaltending called on Mobley (CLE) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed successful. Mobley (CLE) doesn't touch the ball after it hits the backboard.
Okoro (CLE) makes contact with Valanciunas' (NOP) arm that affects his shot near the rim.
Temple (NOP) makes contact to the ball and incidental contact to his Valentine's (CLE) leg after the ball is dislodged.
Okoro (CLE) makes contact to Valanciunas' (NOP) arm that affects his SBQR.
Valentine (CLE) commits a take foul on Graham (NOP).
